Sky_News_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sky News Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News_Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One such guest\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1614}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation's representatives\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1712}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole country\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1741}, {\"ngram\": \"a lift\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1748}, {\"ngram\": \"their return\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's so exciting, I have seen a lot of the parents this morning they are just happy to see their kids return from Europe,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1911, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1815}, {\"ngram\": \"the parents\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1830}, {\"ngram\": \"their kids\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1881}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1900}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are coming back as heroes and they have just given the whole state, the whole country a lift over the last couple of weeks after a tough year.\\\"\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 2062, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"heroes\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1944}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole state\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 1985}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole country\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 2004}, {\"ngram\": \"the last couple\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"weeks\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2041}, {\"ngram\": \"a tough year\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first athletes to emerge from the plane to the cheers of their loved ones were the closing ceremony flagbearers and gold medallists sailor Matt Wearn and swimmer Kaylee McKeown.\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2230, \"end\": 2244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource